<item>
            <title>[LUDOC-306] Document new DNE features for 2.8</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-306</link>
                <project id="10070" key="LUDOC">Lustre Documentation</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;2.8 release will include striped directory feature.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This has means &apos;lfs setstripe&apos; can now take a -c option.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This must be documented.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For initial guidance, lfs.c should be reviewed.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
